ygData.subject: RE: Honeycombs
ygData.msgSnippet: Actually you only have to be level 20 to complete it easily, although I have heard reports of enchanters as low as level 8 doing the quest.
ygData.messageBody:
Actually you only have to be level 20 to complete it easily, although I have
heard reports of enchanters as low as level 8 doing the quest.
